  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Tide Wisps create area denial using Slick Trail and harass from reach with their tendril. In water they outpace most of what they fight and exploit that speed to avoid retaliation. On land they are less effective but useful for placing Difficult Terrain at chokepoints or approaches. A Cooperative Tide Wisp will use Slick Trail to protect the summoner's position rather than chasing targets — a reasonable instinct that benefits from explicit instruction to confirm.</p>"
